      %h3 Ben Schwarz
      %p.position President
    %div.bio
      %p Ben funds his love of good food (at home) and sake (in bars) by designing sophisticated web applications using standards-based technology.
      %p He organised Railscamp 6, in Melbourne, helped run the Melbourne Ruby user group for a couple of years and more recently joined the W3C CSS Working group as an 'invited expert'. Otherwise, he runs <a href="http://theint.ro">The Intro</a>, which he runs to facilitate affordable, professional web focused events that would not exist otherwise.
    %div.contact
      %a{href: 'http://twitter.com/benschwarz'} @benschwarz
